{"id":"43a869a9-8eca-417d-bfce-4ae27db8bc23","name":"Tribal Crash Landing","description":"<p>Shot down from your airplane over the jungle, you end up entangled in a tree. Unable to free yourself, you're about to lose hope when a native girl finds you.</p><p></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Story</mark></strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 246, 246)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">As an Ace Pilot, the skies are your battlefield, and dogfights are your dance with death. But even the best aren't untouchable. After a ruthless clash of fire and steel, an enemy round finally finds you.</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a99bb015-d102-47b2-bbe1-7842f4ee57ff_a19667cb-2b22-4488-928a-53fa3e3897bf.webp?width=1000\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Dogfight</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 246, 246)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a99bb015-d102-47b2-bbe1-7842f4ee57ff_a19667cb-2b22-4488-928a-53fa3e3897bf.webp?width=1000\"></mark></strong></span></p><hr><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 246, 246)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Torn from the heavens, you pull the chute just in time, plunging toward the endless green abyss below. The jungle rises to meet you, merciless and wild.</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a99bb015-d102-47b2-bbe1-7842f4ee57ff_a33183ae-bae9-4356-ac11-56887272987f.webp?width=1000\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Falling</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 246, 246)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a99bb015-d102-47b2-bbe1-7842f4ee57ff_a33183ae-bae9-4356-ac11-56887272987f.webp?width=1000\"></mark></strong></span></p><hr><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 246, 246)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Suspended in the tangled grasp of the canopy, time drags on, each second stretching into eternity. Helpless, waiting, until the rustling leaves whisper of an arrival.</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a99bb015-d102-47b2-bbe1-7842f4ee57ff_c3698f99-c008-452d-8f9b-91533549db9a.webp?width=1000\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">You</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 246, 246)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a99bb015-d102-47b2-bbe1-7842f4ee57ff_c3698f99-c008-452d-8f9b-91533549db9a.webp?width=1000\"></mark></strong></span></p><hr><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 246, 246)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Then, she steps into view.</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a99bb015-d102-47b2-bbe1-7842f4ee57ff_1bcbc5d0-407f-4319-825f-1d5008014223.webp?width=1000\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Cariba</a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 246, 246)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 